name: [SN] Sovetsky Soyuz - Leader of the Northern Parliament | Azur Lane | LoRA
description:
[SN] Sovetsky Soyuz - Leader of the Northern Parliament | Azur Lane | LoRA

The battleship Sovetsky Soyuz is the lead ship of the project 23 type "Sovetsky Soyuz".

This LoRA will allow you, comrades, to recreate this beautiful milady of the Soviet fleet.

The quality may not always be what you expect, due to the small number of images with this character.
LoRA is trained on two character concepts (the old character image and the new one). So when you add the hat keyword, you can get the old concept.

Should activate with:

sovetsky soyuz \(azur lane\)

Recommended parameters:

  • LoRA weight: 0.6-0.9

  • Sampling method: Euler a or DPM++ 2M Karras or SDE

  • Sampling steps: 28

  • CFG Scale: 4-8

  • Upscaler: Latent

  • Denoising strength: 0.55
